hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2F123611_067922c56781f1446bdf418488f4541d.jpg&h=3d2e1bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身盧德昌以大專政關成員身份落區，本身已經少落區，又無人理佢！點知有官司在身就放棄消失。<br />\n到公民黨劉家衡，落區一個月有多，又正面追擊鄭泳舜，又搞放映會，日日街站。<br />\n你個吳文遠無啦啦空降鄧曉文？<br />\n你真係當坐監係CV丫？<br />\n你地社記當社區工作係咩丫？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:55:00.000Z","msg":"只係識叫人入錢入錢入錢 , 上次劉家衡在西營盤已經俾社民連逼走過一次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b68f1cd5b42bca8bcf286308a2c8c61d8606b09","tid":1593372,"uid":318369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4beefa5654016508781f99073e84ad5529e9cc2f","tid":1593372,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"有無人支持miss pun 出選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用寫真踢走舜舜"},{"pid":"dd18bbdbff4711205c288dc38231ab6a6a4ad8eb","tid":1593372,"uid":43126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"要救南昌北就要逼到鄧曉文退"},{"pid":"989164fff3b625db03ce6cbec5d13bcf279782eb","tid":1593372,"uid":236710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"永續社運"},{"pid":"efce2a08aec70e4d63363424bc924053e467f73c","tid":1593372,"uid":237625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd18bbdbff4711205c288dc38231ab6a6a4ad8eb","tid":1593372,"uid":43126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"要救南昌北就要逼到鄧曉文退"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"同意 好似大學區咁 民意都支持劉家衡就唔應該退<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5626b912d7249ec8e6ee41383ebfbfd9da46d7f","tid":1593372,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"選舉有得鬥先見真障好似李卓人咁空降係冇用"}]}